criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male ≥ 40 years old; postmenopausal female;

          -  Patients scheduled to undergo valvular replacement or repair;

          -  Patients providing written informed consent;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with definite coronary artery disease history (Prior myocardial infarction,
             percutaneous coronary intervention or CABG);

          -  Patients with objective evidence of myocardial ischemia;

          -  Underwent CTA or ICA in 6 months;

          -  With contraindications to CTA/ICA (allergic to contrast medium, peripheral arterial
             occlusive disease, chronic kidney disease with estimated glomerular filtration rate
             (eGFR) less than 15ml/min.1.73m2 )
